flowchart TD
    Start((Start)) --> A{Has Valid JWT?}
    A -- No --> B[Display Login Page]
    B --> C[User enters credentials]
    C --> D[Authenticate against PostgreSQL]
    D -- Success --> E[Issue JWT Token]
    D -- Fail --> B
    E --> F[Dashboard / Identify Tab]
    A -- Yes --> F
    
    F --> G{Select Action}
    
    G -- Identify Media --> H[Upload Short Query Clip]
    H --> I[FastAPI decodes via FFmpeg]
    I --> J[Generate STFT Audio Hashes]
    J --> K[Query DB & Compute Temporal Offset]
    K --> L{Audio Match > 35%?}
    L -- Yes --> M[Return Audio Match]
    L -- No --> N[Generate Video pHashes]
    N --> O[Search BK-Tree Hamming < 10]
    O --> P[Calculate Combined Confidence]
    P --> M
    M --> Z((End Process))
    
    G -- Register Media --> Q{Is Role Mod/Admin?}
    Q -- No --> R[Show Access Denied]
    Q -- Yes --> S[Upload High Quality Reference]
    S --> T[Extract ALL Hashes & Frames]
    T --> U[Batch Insert into PostgreSQL]
    U --> Z
    
    G -- Admin Panel --> V{Is Role Admin?}
    V -- No --> R
    V -- Yes --> W[Fetch User List]
    W --> X[Update Roles / Activate Users]
    X --> Z
